  "text": {
    "en": {
      "name": "Dogmatikalamity Alba System",
      "effect": "\"Fallen of Albaz\" + 6 monsters in your GY with different names\nMust first be Fusion Summoned. Can attack all monsters your opponent controls, once each. Cannot declare an attack unless you send 1 card from your Extra Deck to the GY. Once per turn, if you control this Fusion Summoned monster and have 6 or more Fusion Monsters in your GY with different names that mention \"Fallen of Albaz\" as material: You can send all cards in both players' Extra Decks to the GY.",
      "official": false
    },
    "ja": {
